subSubSection.paragraph:
Remarks . This species, originally described from the Hyrcan Nature Reserve in SE Azerbaijan (
Golovatch 1980
), seems to be endemic to Hyrcania within both the Republic of Azerbaijan’s southeastern part and northwestern Iran ( Golovatch 1980 , 1981 ).
